{"tid":895902,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"[MTR痴漢]點先可以識到佢?","createTime":"2018-11-09T14:41:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-21T13:34:56.000Z","uid":90577,"like":1,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"9e02dff65961c8b990b285295fd8b3a12e43c393","tid":895902,"uid":90577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T14:41:02.000Z","msg":"以前都有試過係MTR多次遇見同一個女仔,但之後都冇下文<br />\n今次又係咁<br />\n冇幾耐之前開始,搭MTR放工間中會遇到個女仔<br />\n佢樣一般般,衣著都好普通,次次見佢都係深綠色長外套+牛仔褲<br />\n認得佢主要係因為次次見佢,佢都同個師奶中女同事一齊<br />\n我同佢都係搭綠色線放工,師奶通常中途落車<br />\n我同佢都係太子落車,佢可能同我一樣住太子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n今日OT到8:30放工又撞到佢地<br />\n我企係佢地附近<br />\n唔知係唔係我多心,佢地傾傾下計好似望咗我幾下咁,都唔知係唔係笑我毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁既環境,點先可以識到佢??<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc2392c0c9c9a0b8038f5c2aa5b1728228080d6b","tid":895902,"uid":90577,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T15:43:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6cd85378c248cfd31276ffafeabbde290de0e26b","tid":895902,"uid":220068,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T16:00:41.000Z","msg":"OT都撞到係幾有機喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n等中女落車就去馬啦 機會係唔等人架"},{"pid":"2c54e6cbc1c5875a883fb434a158716ac5a0e7f6","tid":895902,"uid":90577,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T16:00:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/as